This Python-based command-line game allows you to experience the excitement of playing a slot machine right from your terminal.

Features

User Interaction: Interact with the game through the terminal, making it easy to play.
Customisation: Adjust the number of lines to bet on and the bet amount per line to suit your preference.
Randomised Spins: Each spin generates random symbols, ensuring every game is unique.
Winnings Calculation: The game calculates your winnings based on the symbols aligned on the pay lines.
Simple and Enjoyable: Experience a simple yet entertaining game.

How to Play

Deposit: Start by depositing an initial amount of money.
Place Bet: Choose the number of lines to bet on and the amount to bet per line.
Spin: Watch the fruit machine spin and see if you win!
Repeat: Keep playing until you decide to quit.

Requirements
Python 3.x

How to Run

Clone this repository to your local machine.
Navigate to the directory containing the game files.
Run the slots_game.py file using Python: python slots-machine-game.py

Contributions
Contributions are welcome! If you have any suggestions, bug fixes, or additional features you'd like to see added to the game, feel free to open an issue or submit a pull request.
